{"tid":624973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺特區政府係專登放任南亞人問題唔理？","createTime":"2018-04-11T05:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T11:48:26.000Z","uid":38671,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5980827d017deb1199da12f49217c8dcf3a80f94","tid":624973,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:29:49.000Z","msg":"明明唔係所謂「中國人」，要處理唔會觸及港中矛盾<br />\n<br />\n明明而家政府行政主導，政府要做野區區一個張超雄可以阻到咩？<br />\n<br />\n明明好易得民心，就偏偏唔做，由得社會崩壞，你話唔係專登唔做都唔信啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0186d97ed03d7d06a68460c985d389886b38224a","tid":624973,"uid":45353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:36:58.000Z","msg":"跟非洲人一樣<br />\n<br />\n同中國有外交政策<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔覺近年黑鬼都不正常多"},{"pid":"1ebcc4cf7f1208ebc897706d0eeea71342cda967","tid":624973,"uid":99205,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:57:30.000Z","msg":"支共港府做左幾多陰質野想逼害香港人<br />\n<br />\n除左放蹤南亞人大把啦<br />\n<br />\n每日150個在港低端人口吸血,獲取納稅人福利<br />\n<br />\n不斷既超級大白象工程利益輸送，對本港商貿無建樹只係維持GDP<br />\n<br />\n同地產商勾結，半允許囤地黑社會做野燒山<br />\n<br />\n巧立名目創新科技養一班大陸公司同人材但對本港又係零收益<br />\n<br />\n放任公營交通工具有大量盈餘而只升不減機制，誓要榨取市民每一分每一毫<br />\n<br />\n財政方面完全肥上瘦下，將M形社會推動極緻<br />\n<br />\n配合大陸風氣，各層面全力做假不做事，少做少錯<br />\n<br />\n對市民既民生設施由回歸後完全停滯不前<br />\n如熟食市場,清潔同醫療既監管同外判問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢條片較新既鏗鏘集<br />\n支共港府早前裁撒兩局（市政局、區域市政局），將所有行政權力攬住，將所有撥款變左一次過<br />\n形式各類只做數及每年不斷胡亂增加行政費推高撥款既荒謬事日益增加<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CsxTSTrsk0s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCsxTSTrsk0s&d=a3%2FA6laLgyZZ0mbNJ%2FLrwrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8fb08e3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CsxTSTrsk0s</a>"},{"pid":"9d81eaba369afae621ebc0405916d2a920e93248","tid":624973,"uid":44562,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:59:47.000Z","msg":"政府理過啲咩問題 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad6683239560158130c1029c7d85e44e283a535","tid":624973,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:22:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83725f6f2d2a4333e94385acc6caa96d0058bd70","tid":624973,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:38:32.000Z","msg":"跟本就係"},{"pid":"df73271bd7bc447c7ff49a44383f181fa4839872","tid":624973,"uid":18251,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:50:04.000Z","msg":"用嚟混淆新移民問題，等我地仇恨南亞而忽略左大陸新移民。"},{"pid":"36b1b71892939bec6bccb57836da72483f54bbb0","tid":624973,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:55:12.000Z","msg":"個政府除左千億基建之外仲有咩會理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n民生? Who cares?"},{"pid":"20864454973e26d03eec9810759996f75d42cd45","tid":624973,"uid":111229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:01:09.000Z","msg":"留名 個post同我名近似 <br />\n利申：支持趕走假難民"},{"pid":"21dc41a31b088f068d00b733fe3066a84d72b64a","tid":624973,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:11:01.000Z","msg":"販民絕對有份助長蝻亞狗<br />\n<br />\n次次建制提出禁閉營，販民一撚定用人權理由反對"},{"pid":"b9e386aa5b1f4e953927ef1b5cab5c42de44054f","tid":624973,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21dc41a31b088f068d00b733fe3066a84d72b64a","tid":624973,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:11:01.000Z","msg":"販民絕對有份助長蝻亞狗<br />\n<br />\n次次建制提出禁閉營，販民一撚定用人權理由反對"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"扯貓尾啫<br />\n飯乜撚嘢民呀？<br />\n你講啲B隊？"},{"pid":"91c261cba0664a9dc8efe565a4f1404d440928f3","tid":624973,"uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-